data.description: LOOK AT THIS VIEW! Welcome to this exceptional home located in the 55+ Terramor Community, where modern luxury meets breathtaking vistas. Nestled in a tranquil and picturesque neighborhood, this property boasts a perfect blend of elegance and contemporary design, making it the ideal place to call home. Upon entering, you'll be captivated by the spacious and inviting open floor plan that effortlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. Sunlight pours in through large windows, creating an atmosphere of warmth and comfort. The heart of this home is the stunning gourmet kitchen, adorned with gleaming quartz countertops, a chef's dream come true, with its ample counter space and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, it's a culinary enthusiast's delight. One of the standout features of this residence is the captivating view it offers. Step outside to your private oasis, where you'll be greeted by an expansive outdoor living space. The generous patio area provides a front-row seat to nature's beauty, with unobstructed views that change with the seasons. Inside, the home is filled with luxurious upgrades and finishes, showcasing meticulous attention to detail. From custom lighting fixtures to custom flooring, every element of the interior exudes quality and sophistication. The master suite is a true sanctuary, featuring a spa-like en-suite bathroom, a spacious walk-in closet, and its own private view. This property has been thoughtfully designed with energy-efficient features and Solar that is paid for, ensuring both comfort and convenience. The layout includes ample storage options, a two-car garage, and easy access to nearby amenities. In summary, this home with its open floor plan and stunning views offers a lifestyle of luxury and comfort. It's a place where every detail has been carefully curated to provide an unparalleled living experience. Terramor community boasts state-of-the-art amenities, including miles of trails for nature enthusiasts, two exceptional clubhouses for social gatherings, a refreshing pool and spa for relaxation, sport courts for active pursuits, a 24-hour gym for fitness enthusiasts, outdoor cooking spaces for culinary adventures, game rooms for entertainment, and much more. Conveniently located near the 15 freeway, this offers easy access to markets and shopping centers. Schedule your private showing today and experience the lifestyle you've been dreaming of. This is truly a must see home and community.
